summary: Detective Pikachu was super good.   Cute child Imagination Story below: [[MORE]] In other news. My three year old can watch...
caption:
Detective Pikachu was super good. 

Cute child Imagination Story below:

In other news. My three year old can watch Pacific Rim (Don’t judge my Parenting! There is a story there!) but Charizard was too scary … Granted theater are way more immersive than theater.

Anyway, he was scared, we left. and he hung out lobby, me thinking we were done and I was going to have to go back in and tell my husband we had to leave,  …

 but then my son went over to the Pikachu in the photo-op, and pretended to catch him.Then he looked up at me, with all sincerely, holding up an imaginary pokeball, with an imaginary Pikachu in it, and told me Pikachu was going to come with us to the movie and protect him!!

Here he is with his “Tiny brother” and the Pikachu that helped him brave the movie.

Detective Pikachu was super good.
